rit empowerment in Judges and Samuel, and communal possession in the prophets. Carlson also surveys apotropaic texts and spirit myths in early Jewish literature—including the Dead Sea Scrolls. In this volume, two recent scholarly trends in biblical studies converge: investigations into notions of evil and of the self. The result is a synthesizing project, useful to biblical scholars and those of early Judaism and Christianity alike.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aRELIGION / Biblical Criticism & Interpretation / Old Testament.2bisacsh  aHebrew Bible.  aSecond Temple Judaism.  ademons.  aspirit possession.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishz978311099454408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022z9783110994537oZDB-23-DGF0 cEPUBz97831106700660 cprintz978311066934340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311067003540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110670035423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110670035/original  a978-3-11-076682-0  DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099454-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2